reviewText: I really enjoyed watching this movie.  It's one the entire family will enjoy.  The young actors were excellent and worked very well together.  It was fun watching them as they tried to locate items and beat the other teams.  I'll enjoy watching this movie again and again.
This is a good movie I suggest watching if you have seen any of eric hendershot's work he Is a great director and I hope he becomes famous soon
